node.title: Cordons lifted in Mt Maunganui as police search for a man
node.description: Police asked some residents to stay indoors this afternoon as they try and locate a man in the central area of Mount Maunganui.
node.content:
["Police asked some residents to stay indoors this afternoon as they try and locate a man in the central area of Mount Maunganui.", "", "
\nPhoto: RNZ / Richard Tindiller\n
", "Police said earlier in a statement that they were attending a serious incident in the Bedford Place area.", "There were concerns for the wellbeing of the man who police are now trying to find.", "As a precaution, an area was cordoned off, and residents were asked to stay indoors.", "Police are still searching for the person involved, but the cordons have now been lifted in the area."]
